3. The third-party `liblog4cpp.so` distributed in `estun_libs` is subject to
   LGPL-2.1-only. See `estun_libs/LICENSES/LGPL-2.1.txt` and
   `estun_libs/THIRD_PARTY_NOTICES.md`.
4. If a file or package contains a more specific license notice, that notice
   governs the corresponding material.

For additional repository-level context, also review `README.md`,
`estun_libs/LICENSE`, `estun_libs/REDISTRIBUTION.md`, and
`estun_libs/THIRD_PARTY_NOTICES.md`.
